Would you not...

199
00:11:45.738 --> 00:11:47.471
Come on. He loves it.

200
00:11:47.473 --> 00:11:49.573
One of them. kinda.
I...

201
00:11:50.875 --> 00:11:52.809
Hey. Hey.
Shit!

202
00:11:52.811 --> 00:11:55.212
(SCOFFS)
Oh. can I... miss?

203
00:11:55.214 --> 00:11:57.414
All right. well. see ya.

204
00:11:57.416 --> 00:11:59.783
Oh. god.
I'm so allergic to dogs.

205
00:11:59.785 --> 00:12:01.752
Next to the place where I get my pedicure...

206
00:12:01.754 --> 00:12:04.288
