207
00:12:04.290 --> 00:12:07.524
I know you guys think I have the worst
fashion sense ever. but I did find...

208
00:12:07.526 --> 00:12:10.260
- I like vintage.
- I found this really awesome bag.

209
00:12:10.262 --> 00:12:13.764
